personalInfo.title: JSON oriented resume generator for IT professionals

summary:
You are about to use cre8ive.cv ‚Äì a tool for generating a customizable and easily editable resume. Its data layer is a pure JSON which can be exported and reimported (including photo in base64). The app respects your privacy ‚Äì no personal data is stored on the server side after rendering your JSON to PDF. For extra security you can also self-host it on your own local machine.

Any feedback? In order to contact the project's author use the details below or create an issue on the project's GitHub repository.

skills.name: Features
items: All data in one exportable JSON
Uses localStorage, update made after each change
No personal data are stored on the server
Progress is kept until you "Clear All Data", no saving is needed
Up to 4 skills groups with resizable widths
